{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一章讲述现代特种兵项少龙在酒吧与八四一部队教官黑面神发生冲突并将其击败，随后与酒吧皇后周香媚一夜缠绵。次日被军机女秘书郑翠芝以公报私仇的方式派往科学院参加实验。项少龙被送入地底实验室，见到时空计划所长马克及其助手方廷、谢枝敏。马克告知他将被送往公元前246年的秦朝，利用时间炉产生能量黑洞穿越时空。项少龙被绑在金属箱内注射药物后送入时间炉，但实验过程中力场失控，时间炉爆裂，整座地底实验室被炸毁，所有人员无一幸免。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_bao",
      "speaker_name": "犄豹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有多少人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "小张",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "龙哥快给我们出这口鸟气！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_man_niu",
      "speaker_name": "蛮牛",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是八四一部队的教官黑面神，竟斗胆挑惹我们的冰霜靓女。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扶他们进去让小弟表演一下身手！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "speaker_name": "黑面神",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一个对一个，还是一起上！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "text": "对着你这种角式，我什么都没有所谓，悉随尊便。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "小张",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小心点！这小子很厉害。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_man_niu",
      "speaker_name": "蛮牛",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "黑面神后面那两个人是本地洪馆最辣的两个冠军拳手，他们今次是有备而战，全心落我们的颜脸。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_man_niu",
      "text": "叫他们袖手旁观，我有信心单独解决这三个人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "speaker_name": "黑面神",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！我忍你很久了，上次你在野猫卡拉ok打伤了我们十多人，今天我便和你算算旧账。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "text": "给我来支鲜奶，让我教训完黑面神后解渴。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_shen_de_shou_xia",
      "speaker_name": "黑面神的人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子要使出吃奶力气了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来！一齐上。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！你好！我会要你好看！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "周香媚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要带人家到那里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "text": "当然是回家啦，我怎够钱付酒店的昂贵租金。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项队长你尚有十五分钟时间梳洗，宪兵部的装甲车在大门外等你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "周香媚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "衰人！快来！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "你吓唬我吗？打场架又会这么大件事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁说和打架有关，是科学院那边要我们体能最好的特种人员去做实验，我见你昨晚那么英勇，体能好得那么惊人，便向指挥你，指挥已签发了手令哩！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "但今天我仍在放假！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我的项队长，没有任务才可以放假，军人二十四小时都属于国家的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "唉！昨晚我这么勇猛，还不是为了你，你是真不知还是假不知呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "周香媚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你在和谁说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你在骗人！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "我怎会骗你，我项少龙日日夜夜都想着你，只是没说出来吧了！你可知道！你──",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好了！迟些再说吧！最多你只做一天的实验白老鼠，下次我找另外的人去好了。快换衣服。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我又不是病人，自己可以走路。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "护士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乖乖的做个好孩子，我不但知你不是病人，还知道你比一条牛更要强壮。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi",
      "text": "嘿！你叫什么名字，怎样可找到你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ting_bo_shi",
      "speaker_name": "方廷博士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我是方廷博士，她是谢枝敏博士，是这时空计划的总工程师马克所长的助手。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_fang_ting_bo_shi",
      "text": "这是什么一回事？至少应告诉我来这里干什么吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_zhi_min_bo_shi",
      "speaker_name": "谢枝敏博士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！一切都很安全，至于细节，马所长会亲自告诉你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ting_bo_shi",
      "speaker_name": "方廷博士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "军人的天职是为国家服务，项队长能成为时空计划第一个真人试验品，应感到荣幸才对，来！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我就是马克所长，项队长感觉如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "感觉就像一条被送往屠场的畜牲，还不知那是宰猪还是宰牛的屠场。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项队长真会说笑。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你对我们国家那段时期的比较熟悉一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "这和做实验有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先回答我的问题。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "我对知得不多，不过最近看了秦始皇那出电影，对他的阿房宫和放纵的声色生活非常羡慕，又看了几本战国和秦始皇的书",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嘿！这就行了，就是大秦帝国，公元前二百四十六年秦王政即位的第一年。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "我的天！你在说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "朋友！你也不知多么幸运，竟然能成为人类上第一个可返回过去的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "你",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "待会你便会被送进时间炉里，只要我按动一个钮子，装在炉底的氢聚变反应炉会在三十六小时内，积聚了足够的能量，在炉内的热核里产生一个能量的黑洞，破开了时空，那时磁场输送器会把你送回公元前的世界里，你说那是多么奇妙的一件事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "你不是在说笑吧。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然不是说笑，我已成功把十二只白老鼠、两只猴子送回过去，又安全无恃把它们带回来，只可惜它们都不能告诉我是否确实到过那里去，和身处其间的感受。所以才要请军部供应我们体能最好的战士来做实验品，那个人就是你项少龙。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "我不同意，我要立即脱离军队。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要慰张，你只会在那里停畀不到十秒钟的时间，就像发了一个短暂的梦，我只要你记着梦里曾发生过的事。可以注射了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_cha_yan_jiu_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "监察研究员",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "时间炉内的力能失常地攀升，请马所长指示是否应立即关闭能源。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克所长",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "紧急措施第五项，立即执行！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    }
  ],
